cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO 

The paper deals with depth estimation from light field data using a fully convolutional neural network architecture. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The use of a neural network also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of real-world recordings suggests the involvement of robotics (cs.RO) sub-category.
